HR Onboarding Automation Using DocuSign 

Background 
AcmeTech currently handles employee onboarding manually. HR sends agreements through email and tracks signatures separately. 
This process works for small hiring volumes but becomes difficult to manage during rapid hiring periods. 
The goal is to automate document signing using DocuSign so onboarding becomes faster, more consistent, and easier to track. 

Problem Statement 
The current onboarding process depends on manual coordination between HR and new employees. 
 This creates challenges such as delayed agreement completion, missing approvals, lack of visibility into signing progress, and increased manual effort for HR teams. 

Objective 
Build a backend integration service that automates the employee agreement signing workflow. 
 The service should receive onboarding details, create a DocuSign envelope, apply signing order rules, track document progress, and store onboarding status. 

Scope 
This solution focuses only on backend integration. 
 External HR systems are not included. 
 The onboarding request will be simulated using API calls. 

Business Rules 
Standard enployee?--->HR Manager--->Employee
Manager or Above?--->HR Manager--->Employee(manager)--->Department Head 

Expected Outcome 
The onboarding workflow becomes automated. 
 HR no longer needs to manually manage document approvals. 